metadata.name: BLOCKBUSTER
metadata.description:
The year is 1999.  You are standing at the counter of a small Blockbuster franchise outside of the mall.  It smells like Doritos and musty carpets in here.  Your ass is sweating already while waiting in line.  You have to poop, but the bathroom is out of order again - gonna have to race home.  What movie are you going to rent?  

Digital 3D
3000x3000
